---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms" description="MaaxGen terms of use draft.">
  <section class="page-hero page-hero--accent">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">Draft for counsel review</p>
      <h1>Terms of use</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        This placeholder sets a basic terms structure for the MaaxGen website. Review with counsel before public launch.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose legal-copy">
      <h2>Website use</h2>
      <p>
        This website provides general information about MaaxGen services. The content is not a guarantee of results, legal advice, financial advice, or a substitute for a signed service agreement.
      </p>

      <h2>Service inquiries</h2>
      <p>
        Submitting a form or booking a call does not create a client relationship. Scope, pricing, timelines, and responsibilities should be confirmed in a written agreement before work begins.
      </p>

      <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        Website copy, visual design, logos, and other brand assets belong to MaaxGen or their respective owners unless otherwise noted. Do not copy, reproduce, or reuse site materials without permission.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party links and tools</h2>
      <p>
        The site may link to third-party tools for booking, forms, analytics, or content. MaaxGen is not responsible for third-party policies, uptime, or content.
      </p>

      <h2>Case studies and results</h2>
      <p>
        Case study content may include placeholders until client approval. Results vary by business, offer, market, budget, and execution. Replace placeholder stories with approved client copy before launch.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Add the preferred legal contact email and business mailing address before publishing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
